fi.zudoku.hydraulic.util

Class BitBlob

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.zudoku.hydraulic.util.BitBlob

  • public class BitBlob
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a chunk of bits that can be any length. This is used to help dealing with bits in Java. For example if we want to append less than 8 bits at a time to some byte array.
